{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2646425, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 505011, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是的，有钱谁run", "timestamp": 1633221417, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2646427, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 505011, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "run是什么意思啊 转行吗", "timestamp": 1633221446, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2646435, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 505011, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "硕士按两年的话最贵的美帝也就七八十万（不挥霍），普通家庭一般来说是有这钱的，只是说会大出血但不至于影响生活，更不用说日本欧洲英国更便宜", "timestamp": 1633221741, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2646444, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 505011, "reply_to": 2646435, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 读cs硕士比较容易run吧，去日本、欧洲好像不太容易留下来", "timestamp": 1633222098, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2646447, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 505011, "reply_to": 2646444, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 日欧英挺多设计类牛校的，设计环境国外比国内好得多", "timestamp": 1633222223, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2646506, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 505011, "reply_to": 2646435, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 普通家庭…七八十万还是挺有压力了", "timestamp": 1633223397, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2646578, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 505011, "reply_to": 2646435, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 能拿出7，80万让你去读书的，家庭条件不会太差", "timestamp": 1633224603, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2646596, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 505011, "reply_to": 2646506, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 大中城市中产家庭七八十万出出血应该大多都没问题，大不了就卖房。小城市、县城、农村的普通家庭或者住棚户区的大城市底层土著，拿出七八十万真的很难。🇨🇳很多省份人均存款就5万左右的，而且50％的家庭无任何存款", "timestamp": 1633224776, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2646639, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 505011, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "唉", "timestamp": 1633225193, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2646679, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 505011, "reply_to": 2646435, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 普通家庭。。年收入也没有七八十万", "timestamp": 1633225574, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2646742, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 505011, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如何定义“普通家庭”", "timestamp": 1633226277, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2646846, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 505011, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "并不普通的普通家庭，以及地区和地区之间的收入差距真的很大，哪怕做的是一模一样的工作", "timestamp": 1633227768, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 16, "pid": 505011, "reply": 12, "tag": null, "text": "其实越是家境一般的同学越适合run，家里有钱直接继承家产躺就好了，家里有权整个选调前途光明，而家庭条件一般躺也躺不平，去体制也没前途，同样是进厂打工被资本家剥削，外面挣得更多，剥削还更轻一些，为何不run呢。当然有同学说run需要一定的经济基础，其实大不了本科毕业先去打两年工，攒攒学费然后再run也挺好", "timestamp": 1633221155, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1633227770, "url": "", "vote": {}}}